{"tid":966193,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"每個男人都係一個饑渴嘅人","createTime":"2019-01-02T15:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T06:47:30.000Z","uid":172616,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"817a2183f701ed6d647cdff108f034c2c9bb6dd7","tid":966193,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"點解男人咁鍾意屌閪呢?<br />\n<br />\n因為閪有好飲的閪水, 一個饑渴嘅人, 遇到一池冇人飲過又好飲的閪水, 就會按耐不住想飲。<br />\n<br />\n唔畀佢飲水, 咁佢就會搵其他方法解渴, 例如去飲一啲好多人飲過的水, 水入面唔知會有啲咩菌, 飲完可能會瀨嘢。<br />\n<br />\n又有一些人會去飲自己的尿, 雖然冇飲閪水咁好, 但可以解決一吓燃眉之急。<br />\n<br />\n更有一些人會去飲其他人的尿, 仲會覺得好好飲, 對閪水冇了興趣。<br />\n<br />\n但總括嚟講, 男人都係最希望飲到甘甜的閪水。<br />\n<br />\n完。"},{"pid":"c3c40989e9b4f98392053bdfc3b3a5d207a85d67","tid":966193,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"呢篇嘢係見到一個感情台po有感而發的<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3c906fbd58fab46f4b2455c06016a659824b1e","tid":966193,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"唔好笑"},{"pid":"46c8b112cb9a20934a515a6938242d3c96f432af","tid":966193,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb3c906fbd58fab46f4b2455c06016a659824b1e","tid":966193,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"唔好笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"認真嘢嚟"},{"pid":"48f7004aaadf674400d77aedfbd872ef6eeb5b1d","tid":966193,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46c8b112cb9a20934a515a6938242d3c96f432af","tid":966193,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb3c906fbd58fab46f4b2455c06016a659824b1e","tid":966193,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"唔好笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"認真嘢嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"唔好笑"},{"pid":"5feb1494302a7410995f8f6ccf8c0d